q f17ae5zn&quot; href=&quot;http://www.asteralabs.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;www.asteralabs.com&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Job Responsibilities:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table style=&quot;height: 80px; width: 1080px;&quot; width=&quot;714&quot;&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style=&quot;width: 1065.88px;&quot; width=&quot;77&quot;&gt;Support post-silicon validation of connectivity products, solving lab challenges across hardware and software while collaborating with cross-functional teams&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Qualifications&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table style=&quot;height: 362px; width: 2087px;&quot; width=&quot;1773&quot;&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style=&quot;width: 355.982px;&quot; width=&quot;271&quot;&gt;Support post-silicon validation of connectivity products, solving lab challenges across hardware and software while collaborating with cross-functional teams&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&quot;width: 256.711px;&quot; width=&quot;184&quot;&gt;In B.S. or M.S. in EE or related field&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&quot;width: 290.94px;&quot; width=&quot;214&quot;&gt;Coursework focused in RF/microwave, communication systems.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&quot;width: 252.149px;&quot; width=&quot;180&quot;&gt;Working knowledge of analog and digital circuit design fundametals.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&quot;width: 256.711px;&quot; width=&quot;184&quot;&gt;Lab experience with equipment such as oscilloscopes, Vector Network Analyzer (VNA), and Sourcemeter&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&quot;width: 288.659px;&quot; width=&quot;212&quot;&gt;Scripting or software development in programing languages such as Python (preferred), C/C++ or Java.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&quot;width: 290.972px;&quot; width=&quot;214&quot;&gt;Experience with using python for automation and control of lab instruments&lt;br&gt;Project experience with microcontrollers or using computers as components, such as Arduino/Raspberry Pi projects or building custom PC’s.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;Knowledge of Signal Integrity, S-Parameters, SERDES architecture, Jitter Decomposition&lt;br&gt;Experience working with PCI Express PCIe&amp;nbsp; or other high-speed serial interfaces such as USB&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We know that creativity and innovation happen more often when teams include diverse ideas, backgrounds, and experiences, and we actively encourage everyone with relevant experience to apply, including people of color, LGBTQ+ and non-binary people, veterans, parents, and individuals with disabilities.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
